  "text": "Classification of genes and predictions of biological gene function were performed manually with GO-terms from zebrafish and mouse (Mus musculus). Zebrafish GO-terms were found in Zfin [CITATION_1] . Orthologue search was done in Ensembl (Yates et al., 2016) and GO-terms for mouse were found in MGI [CITATION_2] .",
